        </div>
        <div class="container course-content">
            <div class="course-title">赛图GMAT提升段课程</div>
            <div class="d-flex flex-wrap">
                <div class="course-bg course-one">
                    <div class="course-top top-one d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <img src="./img/course/d1.png" alt="">
                        <span>目标</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-bottom">
                        冲700分
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="course-bg course-two">
                    <div class="course-top top-two d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <img src="./img/course/d2.png" alt="">
                        <span>对象</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="course-bottom">
                        基础段课程结束者或定级测试正确
                        率在75%以上者
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="course-bg course-three">
                    <div class="course-top top-one d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
                        <img src="./img/course/d3.png" alt="">
